<Layout
  title="How To Convert A MemberPress Site To A Native Mobile App"
  description="Converting a MemberPress site into a mobile app can enhance user experience, boost loyalty and retention, and decrease churn rates. Building an app can be easier than expected with tools like MobiLoud Canvas!"
>
  <Nav />

  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 px-4">
